Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡诺恩的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司 镝木没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…看见了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为系统负荷？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我说什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒 剑司
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…龙骨区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么会在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 醒过神来就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:02:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡诺恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卫 翔子 道生哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连老妈也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等因你们而学会了新的共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同将觉醒的力量培育成长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬岛发生敌方力场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护盾减弱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚瑠岛部队 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吝惜弹药 尽量削弱敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来了 彗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上空的护盾完全消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得守住才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月读的SDP覆盖了上空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海中的敌人与Alvis本舰接触
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二磁冠护盾 消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将护盾集中于防空洞区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让岛民登上两侧舰避难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有战斗力都投入了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果作战计划无法继续执行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就转移至D计划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先将重症患者送上舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:04:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 请让我…留在岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镝木 快回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你退下 里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司学长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复原状了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛楚我来背负
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持位置 明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九号机受损的美杜莎修复
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持能量连接及迎击状态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SDP…是八号机的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一人 另一种力量也苏醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机回归原地 作战继续
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天照没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在驾驶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春日井学长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立上学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来的话会连你也同化掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去保护镝木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御门 镝木呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上回来 和另一架机体一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代码重新登录
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四号机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲洋…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考联系…谢谢你 剑司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能允许我…使用岛的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那机体是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认四号机重新登录
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭乘者是…春日井甲洋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了吗 带着新的力量一同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两种力量苏醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种是药 一种是毒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到达未来所需的力量 全都集齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在这里 在这岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要守护 像姐姐他们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要变强 阿卫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算清醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要边睡边指挥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是思考联系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和岛的星核
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦话待会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CDC打算转移至那个逃离计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战继续
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一迎击队 准备锁定目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九号机 用你的SDP给天照增幅力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力 请给我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近藤医生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持防线 我来防止同化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再坚持一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美三香收到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若憎恨就是你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天自己也会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四号机会帮我们挡住头目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二迎击队 攻击敌人包围圈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二号机 维持位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须佐之男 锁定目标
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把天上的敌人给我砍掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于够着了 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想吃掉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也想同化更多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃更多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我吧 你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到你了 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九号机 锁定目标
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 在下降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月读 挡住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 没法开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 机体要被吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须…守护大家
