Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一 第三迎击队 维持位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二号机 须佐之男 开始迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破包围圈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我吃掉你的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利维坦型的利齿崩毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速前进 别放过这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ALVIS 逃离敌人束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对海中的敌人释放残存火力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三迎击队前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击退敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体…好热
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲良 咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须佐之男 收拾掉上空的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈班闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:14:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去 水镜！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奈…学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人 消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢奋勇作战的战士们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也感谢核的忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲的并不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛会回复力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医疗室 紧急运送昏迷的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四号机？难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲洋？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美三香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…明明一直保持思考联系的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲洋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的心还留着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…美三香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会守住…大家的归处的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:18:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核？为何在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡诺恩怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:29.80,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}（N第15营地）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 完全没人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基斯 你那边如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是他们的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆一堆废铁假装在这里而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是根据新联合国的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们应该还在新北京这里没走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电力修复了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地构造很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员集合 他们在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让星核变成对人类有用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是人类重新夺回和平的唯一途径
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留言吗 真是荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无意与诸位作战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.15,0:20:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立即撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则将有灾祸降临
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是广域通信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是造了个夸张的基地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Festum袭来初期建设的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时要防止敌人的读心能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能潜入海里或是藏在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的吧 不休息就没法作战了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不是有意说那种话的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 你睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新北京基地通往地下的隔离壁被打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封锁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们回想起真正应该对付的敌人是谁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.22,0:21:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况不妙 达斯汀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也赶紧前往地底…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳雷因…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达斯汀 天上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在黑暗的道路上前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追寻着光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.18,0:22:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,付出众多牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.62,0:22:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并伴着更多的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将迎来旅途的终点
